"Automatic tasks that move prospects through the recruitment funnel (log, "
"invite, test training, trial review, team offer). The onboarding pipeline "
"view stays available when this is off; only new task automation stops."
msgstr ""
"Automatische taken die prospects door de wervingstrechter leiden "
"(registreren, uitnodigen, proeftraining, stagebeoordeling, teamaanbod). De "
"onboarding-pijplijnweergave blijft beschikbaar wanneer dit uit staat; alleen "
