msgid "Per-cap resolution"
msgstr "Rechtoplossing per recht"

#: src/Modules/Authorization/Admin/AuthChainDebugPage.php:232
msgid ""
"For each cap, three checks: (a) user_can() — the WP layer, which consults "
"baseline role caps + the user_has_cap filter (matrix bridge when active); "
"(b) LegacyCapMapper::evaluate() — the matrix-bridge direct call, bypassing "
"the user_can() pipeline; (c) AuthorizationService::userCanOrMatrix() — the "
"helper that combines both. The \"Failing layer\" column points at which "
"layer is the first to fall."
msgstr ""
"Voor elk recht drie controles: (a) user_can() — de WP-laag, die de "
"basisrolrechten + het user_has_cap-filter raadpleegt (matrixbrug indien "
"actief); (b) LegacyCapMapper::evaluate() — de directe matrixbrug-aanroep, "
"die de user_can()-pijplijn omzeilt; (c) AuthorizationService::"
"userCanOrMatrix() — de helper die beide combineert. De kolom \"Falende "
"laag\" wijst aan welke laag als eerste valt."

