#: src/Modules/Authorization/Admin/MatrixPage.php:370
msgid "Preview changes"
msgstr "Bekijk wijzigingen"

#: src/Modules/Authorization/Admin/MatrixPage.php:372
msgid ""
"The file is parsed in-memory; never written to wp-content/uploads. If your "
"host rejects .xlsx, the .csv path bypasses the Office allowlist entirely."
msgstr ""
"Het bestand wordt in het geheugen verwerkt en nooit weggeschreven naar wp-"
