#: src/Modules/Authorization/Admin/RolesPage.php:264
msgid ""
"Indirect grants come from a functional role mapping. To remove one, either "
"unassign the person from the team or change the functional role's mapping on "
"the Functional Roles admin page."
msgstr ""
"Indirecte toekenningen komen voort uit een functionele-rolkoppeling. Om er "
"een te verwijderen, haal de persoon van het team af of wijzig de koppeling "
"van de functionele rol op de beheerpagina Functionele rollen."

#: src/Modules/Authorization/Admin/RolesPage.php:458
msgid ""
"Full access across the academy. Can manage all entities, assign staff, and "
"configure the system."
msgstr ""
"Volledige toegang binnen de academie. Kan alle entiteiten beheren, staf "
"toewijzen en het systeem configureren."

#: src/Modules/Authorization/Admin/RolesPage.php:460
msgid ""
"Shapes methodology and reviews output. Read-all across the academy plus "
"evaluations management. No player-data editing, no staff reassignment."
msgstr ""
"Vormt de methodiek en beoordeelt de output. Leest alles binnen de academie "
"plus evaluatiebeheer. Geen spelersdata-bewerking, geen staf-herindeling."

#: src/Modules/Authorization/Admin/RolesPage.php:462
msgid ""
"Full control within assigned teams — players, evaluations, activities, "
"goals, and team settings. Scoped to team."
msgstr ""
"Volledige controle binnen toegewezen teams — spelers, evaluaties, "
"activiteiten, doelen en teaminstellingen. Beperkt tot team."

#: src/Modules/Authorization/Admin/RolesPage.php:464
msgid ""
"Evaluate and observe within assigned teams. Can create and edit own "
"evaluations; cannot edit other coaches' evaluations. Scoped to team."
msgstr ""
"Evalueer en observeer binnen toegewezen teams. Kan eigen evaluaties aanmaken "
"en bewerken; kan evaluaties van andere trainers niet bewerken. Beperkt tot "
"team."

#: src/Modules/Authorization/Admin/RolesPage.php:466
msgid ""
"Runs logistics within assigned teams — roster, activities, team settings. No "
"evaluation permissions. Scoped to team."
msgstr ""
"Regelt de logistiek binnen toegewezen teams — selectie, activiteiten, "
"teaminstellingen. Geen evaluatie-rechten. Beperkt tot team."

#: src/Modules/Authorization/Admin/RolesPage.php:468
msgid "Read-only access to players and activities within assigned teams."
msgstr ""
"Alleen-lezen toegang tot spelers en activiteiten binnen toegewezen teams."

#: src/Modules/Authorization/Admin/RolesPage.php:470
msgid ""
"Minimal read-only access within assigned teams. Default authorization for "
"the \"Other\" functional role — see only players and activities of the teams "
"you are assigned to, nothing more."
msgstr ""
"Minimale alleen-lezen toegang binnen toegewezen teams. Standaardautorisatie "
"voor de functionele rol \"Overig\" — bekijk alleen spelers en activiteiten "
"van de teams waaraan je bent toegewezen, niets meer."

#: src/Modules/Authorization/Admin/RolesPage.php:472
msgid ""
"View any player and create scouting evaluations. Can be assigned globally or "
"to specific teams."
msgstr ""
"Bekijk elke speler en maak scouting-evaluaties aan. Kan globaal of aan "
"specifieke teams worden toegewezen."

#: src/Modules/Authorization/Admin/RolesPage.php:474
msgid ""
"Read-only access to linked children's records. Scoped to specific players."
msgstr ""
"Alleen-lezen toegang tot gekoppelde gegevens van kinderen. Beperkt tot "
"specifieke spelers."

#: src/Modules/Authorization/Admin/RolesPage.php:476
msgid ""
"Read-only access to own profile. Auto-derived from tt_players.wp_user_id — "
"not manually grantable."
msgstr ""
"Alleen-lezen toegang tot eigen profiel. Automatisch afgeleid van tt_players."
"wp_user_id — niet handmatig toekenbaar."

