#: src/Modules/Mfa/Wizards/BackupCodesStep.php:59
msgid ""
"These 10 codes let you sign in if you lose your phone. Each code works once. "
"Store them somewhere safe — a password manager, a printed copy in a drawer, "
"anywhere not on the same phone."
